snippet.title: Electric Crayon 3.1.: Super Mario Bros & Friends: When I Grow Up (MS DOS) Gameplay
snippet.description: One of the rarest Mario games out there, this is a game were you can color in Mario and his friends, and even Link from the Legend of Zelda! It's quite interesting.
